@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Chatbot Query (Question Answering)

skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor LightCyan
    BorderColor #0066CC
}

|User|
start
:Type question in chat interface\n(e.g., "What are the features?");
:Click "Send" button\n(Question + Project ID);

|System|
:Receive question request;
:Expand query\n(Add related terms and synonyms);
note right: Query expansion for better retrieval

:Setup vector retriever\n(LangChain + Supabase);

:Create retrieval chain\n(Retrieve + Combine + LLM);

:Invoke chain with question;

:Search relevant documents\nfrom Supabase\n(Similarity search);

:Get top k chunks\n(sorted by similarity);
note right: Most relevant chunks retrieved

:Combine documents\ninto context string;

:Send to OpenAI LLM\n(context + question\n+ system prompt);
note right: LLM generating answer...

:Generate AI answer\n(cited with section numbers);

:Return answer;

|User|
:See loading indicator;
:Receive AI answer in chat;
:See answer with citations\n(e.g., "As per section 3.2.1...");
:Can ask follow-up questions;
stop

@enduml
